OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779466274
OL,3,CSummerland families face anxious wait
OL,4,Cafter fresh inquest hearing concludes
OL,6,FA hearing to determine whether the
OL,7,FAttorney General was right to deny the
OL,8,FSummerland families a fresh inquest
OL,9,Finto the fire, has concluded.
OL,11,FMembers of the 'Justice for
OL,12,FSummerland' group travelled to the
OL,13,Fisland to witness the case, where
OL,14,Ftheir advocates argued a new inquest
OL,15,Finto the deaths of the disaster were
OL,16,F'crucial' to 'finding the truth'.
OL,18,FThe Summerland fire is often referred
OL,19,Fto as the Isle of Man's greatest
OL,20,Fdisaster.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
