PN,39702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779466274
OL,3,CSummerland families face anxious wait
OL,4,Cafter fresh inquest hearing concludes
OL,6,FOn 2 August 1973, three boys set fire
OL,7,Fto a kiosk outside the esteemed
OL,8,Fleisure complex, rapidly spreading
OL,9,Facross the entire building within
OL,10,Fminutes.
OL,12,FFifty people died and many more were
OL,13,Finjured.
OL,15,FAn inquest was then held in 1974, and
OL,16,Fa verdict of 'misadventure' was given
OL,17,Fto those who died.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779466274
OL,3,CSummerland families face anxious wait
OL,4,Cafter fresh inquest hearing concludes
OL,6,FCampaigners say the verdict puts the
OL,7,Fblame on the victims, saying it
OL,8,F'implies they were taking a risk' when
OL,9,Fentering the public building.
OL,11,FOpening with a minutes silence, the
OL,12,Fhearing started with the advocate
OL,13,Frepresenting the families, Steven
OL,14,FCoren.
OL,16,FHe described the current verdict as
OL,17,Fthe 'stain on the records', adding
OL,18,Fthat new forensic methods would
OL,19,F'undoubtedly' lead to a different
OL,20,Fconclusion.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779466274
OL,3,CSummerland families face anxious wait
OL,4,Cafter fresh inquest hearing concludes
OL,6,FPart of his submission also
OL,7,Fhighlighted similarities with
OL,8,Fdisasters such as Hillsborough and the
OL,9,FStardust nightclub fire in Dublin -
OL,10,Fboth examples where fresh inquests
OL,11,Fwere held, and new verdicts returned.
OL,13,FChair of the campaign and Summerland
OL,14,Fsurvivor, Jackie Hallam, described the
OL,15,Ftwo-day hearing as 'harrowing', but
OL,16,Fsaid the families were 'grateful the
OL,17,Fcourt is taking this seriously'.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779466274
OL,3,CSummerland families face anxious wait
OL,4,Cafter fresh inquest hearing concludes
OL,6,FJackie was visiting the island on
OL,7,Fholiday in 1973, aged 13, with her mum
OL,8,FLorna Norton, and her best friend Jane
OL,9,FTallon.
OL,11,FAll three were inside Summerland as
OL,12,Fthe fire spread, but Jackie was the
OL,13,Fonly one to make it out alive,
OL,14,Fsuffering lifelong injuries and
OL,15,Fcontinued distress.
OL,17,FShe said: "I know what it was like in
OL,18,Fthere, I was trapped in there myself.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779466274
OL,3,CSummerland families face anxious wait
OL,4,Cafter fresh inquest hearing concludes
OL,6,F"Loved ones died in such harrowing
OL,7,Fcircumstances, people couldn't even
OL,8,Fimagine, and we are just hopeful that
OL,9,Fthe decision goes our way."
OL,11,FAlso in attendance was Jane Stevenson,
OL,12,Fwho lost her grandmother Anne Barber
OL,13,Fin the fire.
OL,15,FAnne, known as 'Nancy', was visiting
OL,16,Fthe leisure complex with her friend
OL,17,FElsie Stevens, and were the two oldest
OL,18,Fvictims of the fire, aged 68 and 69.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779466274
OL,3,CSummerland families face anxious wait
OL,4,Cafter fresh inquest hearing concludes
OL,6,FJane said her father, David Barber,
OL,7,Ftravelled to the island to identify
OL,8,Fthe bodies, and was 'devastated' by
OL,9,Fthe misadventure verdict.
OL,11,F"He shut down when he came back to the
OL,12,FUK, he couldn't talk about it", she
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,F"We as children were not really told
OL,16,Fmuch about it - anything to do with
OL,17,Fthe Isle of Man deeply upset him."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779466274
OL,3,CSummerland families face anxious wait
OL,4,Cafter fresh inquest hearing concludes
OL,6,FJane travelled to the island for 50th
OL,7,Fanniversary of the fire in 2023, where
OL,8,Fshe then joined the 'Justice for
OL,9,FSummerland' campaign.
OL,11,F"I then started to find out more that
OL,12,Fwas behind Summerland, and various
OL,13,Fthings that I was quite appalled
OL,14,Fabout, and felt I had to get involved
OL,15,Fin the campaign group.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779466274
OL,3,CSummerland families face anxious wait
OL,4,Cafter fresh inquest hearing concludes
OL,6,F"My father then started to open up,
OL,7,Fand I think it was cathartic for him
OL,8,Fto then be able to speak and open up
OL,9,Fall of these things he'd buried for
OL,10,Fthe last 50 years - and he knew we
OL,11,Fwere trying to get a new inquest.
OL,13,F"Sadly he died a couple of weeks ago,
OL,14,Fwhich is upsetting because he'll never
OL,15,Fknow the outcome, but at least he knew
OL,16,Fwe were doing something about it - and
OL,17,Fthat meant the world to me."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779466274
OL,3,CSummerland families face anxious wait
OL,4,Cafter fresh inquest hearing concludes
OL,6,FWhile the Attorney General, Walter
OL,7,FWannenburgh, was not in court for the
OL,8,Fhearing, he was represented by
OL,9,Fadvocate Oliver Helfrich.
OL,11,FHe laid out the argument that there is
OL,12,Fa distinct lack of 'new evidence' that
OL,13,Fwould be needed to hold any new
OL,14,Finquest, adding that 'new forensic
OL,15,Ftechniques' wouldn't necessarily lead
OL,16,Fto a different outcome.
OL,18,FArguing in favour of the original
OL,19,Finquiry, he said there was no evidence
OL,20,Fthat it was 'anything other than an
OL,21,Faccurate report of the fire'.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779466274
OL,3,CSummerland families face anxious wait
OL,4,Cafter fresh inquest hearing concludes
OL,6,FAddressing the misadventure verdicts,
OL,7,Fhe argued it did not 'imply blame' on
OL,8,Fthe individuals, and said the families
OL,9,Fmay have 'misunderstood' the term.
OL,11,FHe also highlighted the key
OL,12,Fdifferences in referencing other
OL,13,Fdisasters - saying their application
OL,14,Fis 'too reliant' on comparisons with
OL,15,FHillsborough and Stardust - when in
OL,16,Fthis particular case it should be seen
OL,17,Fthrough the lens of the Isle of Man.
OL,19,FIn a written statement, a spokesperson
OL,20,Ffor the Isle of Man Government said:
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779466274
OL,3,CSummerland families face anxious wait
OL,4,Cafter fresh inquest hearing concludes
OL,6,F"The Summerland fire continues to have
OL,7,Fa lasting impact on families,
OL,8,Fsurvivors and the wider community.
OL,9,FAhead of the 50th anniversary of the
OL,10,Fdisaster in 2023 Chief Minister Alfred
OL,11,FCannan MHK apologised on behalf of the
OL,12,FIsle of Man Government for 'the pain
OL,13,Fand suffering felt by everyone
OL,14,Faffected' by the Summerland fire.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779466274
OL,3,CSummerland families face anxious wait
OL,4,Cafter fresh inquest hearing concludes
OL,6,F"We understand that campaigners wish
OL,7,Fto challenge the decision of His
OL,8,FMajesty's Attorney General that there
OL,9,Fshould not be a new inquest into the
OL,10,Fdisaster and that a petition of
OL,11,Fdoleance hearing is taking place in
OL,12,Fthe Isle of Man High Court of Justice.
OL,14,F"As this matter is being considered
OL,15,Findependently through the established
OL,16,Flegal process it would not appropriate
OL,17,Fto comment further at this time."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39714
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779466274
OL,3,CSummerland families face anxious wait
OL,4,Cafter fresh inquest hearing concludes
OL,6,FAn Isle of Man judge - known as the
OL,7,FFirst Deemster - reserved judgement in
OL,8,Fthe case, saying he would hand down a
OL,9,Fwritten ruling at a later date.
OL,11,FAndrew Corlett concluded by describing
OL,12,Fthe disaster as 'very upsetting for a
OL,13,Flot of people, and to the Isle of Man
OL,14,Fas a whole'.
OL,16,FThe families are continuing to fund
OL,17,Fthe campaign through their
OL,18,F'CrowdJustice' page.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
